::KitKat::

She turned and walked into the base.  She was heavily damaged. She 
was having trouble keeping her eyes open fromt he loss of fluid.  She 
turned and saw Drillbit on the floor.  She used what little strength 
she had to drag him to the CR chambers.  She sat on the side of the 
CR chamber and fell unconsious.
